      "description": "Offered for sale is a 2008 Porsche Cayman S, a mid-engine platform featuring the 3.4L M97.21 naturally aspirated flat-six. This powerplant delivers 295 hp and 251 lb-ft of torque, mated to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The vehicle exhibits excellent mechanical health, with the VarioCam Plus system providing a broad, linear torque curve and a crisp 7,200 RPM redline. The chassis remains composed, utilizing a MacPherson strut suspension that retains factory-spec damping and bushings for optimal lateral grip. Recent service includes a cooling system overhaul with a high-flow water pump and a comprehensive bore scoring inspection to ensure cylinder wall integrity. This 987.1 generation example represents the pinnacle of hydraulic steering feedback and analog driver engagement, finished in a classic Arctic Silver Metallic over a well-bolstered black leather interior.",
